  </div>

  <div class="launch-info">
    <div class="launch-icon">🌙</div>
    <div class="launch-text">
      Launching on <strong>Eid al-Adha, May 27, 2026</strong>. Waitlist members get early access and a special launch offer. iOS only.
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

